ActFinancial Administration Act
SubjectRemission Order in Respect of a Transfer of a Sahtu Dene and Metis Settlement Corporation's Assets under a Self-Government Agreement
PrecisREMISSION ORDER IN RESPECT OF A TRANSFER OF A SAHTU DENE AND METIS SETTLEMENT CORPORATION'S ASSETS UNDER A SELF-GOVERNMENT AGREEMENT in order to enable a settlement corporation within the meaning of the Sahtu Dene and Metis Comprehensive Land Claim Agreement to cease to exist and all of its assets to be transferred to a Sahtu Dene and Metis government under the self-government agreement that creates the Sahtu Dene and Metis government, without tax implications.
